title: Emmett Brickowski
text: Hello, I’m Emmett, a construction worker and totally normal guy. My favourite TV show is ‘Where are my Pants?’ and my favourite song is ‘Everything is Awesome’. I also like to drink reasonably-priced coffee. My best friends are Lucy, Vitruvius, Batman, Princess Unkitty, Benny, Good Cop, and Planty.
